  "logNo": "223044441442",
  "title": "신뢰가 필수인 부동산중개인, 프로필 명함으로 완성하세요.",
  "date": "2023-03-15",
  "addDate": "2023. 3. 15.",
  "categoryNo": "44",
  "category": "프로필명함",
  "source_url": "https://m.blog.naver.com/cookthedesign/223044441442",
  "content_html": "<div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-79fe2a6e-5407-47d1-a294-7f1bbff19d92\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223044441442/000.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-7ff0d82a-21b6-4c75-9db3-b374105e4777\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-a9b0c998-076b-484d-a5bd-7a9d62c40264\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-\" id=\"SE-13a1998b-703e-4d91-a065-90e054955a10\" style=\"color:#555555;\">(주)파파스컴퍼니이 자신 있게 선보이는 프로필 명함입니다. 자신의 커리어를 알리는데 가장 효과적인 홍보수단이 될 것입니다. 이번에 제작된 프로필 명함을 소개합니다. 출발하겠습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-e67167d3-50e3-4fd2-9bf2-43006260327a\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-\" id=\"SE-96364db7-6a79-4cc8-8d52-fcb067ca8347\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-quotation se-l-quotation_underline\" id=\"SE-89cc89e0-90f2-447d-86e2-4b147f961ea7\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-quotation se-l-quotation_underline\">\n<blockquote class=\"se-quotation-container\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-quote\"><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-dc362d97-8f9f-4635-b947-1129cad7478b\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff-\" id=\"SE-0f5309ce-6340-4bed-8da9-91b6f9429744\" style=\"\">프로필 명함은 자신의 얼굴을 노출하는 업종에 적합한 모바일 명함입니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --></div>\n</blockquote>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-3585bb88-1a65-4dda-b070-cfba37f3a5d7\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-ebdd2e58-a8e7-4316-8cbd-83c7be8104ae\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-\" id=\"SE-a6e7693a-bcd5-4042-837f-b3023227dd7b\" style=\"color:#555555;\">어떤 전문분야에 따라 자신의 얼굴을 노출하여 신뢰도를 높이고 커리어를 어필하는데 필요한 업종이 있습니다. 지금 아래의 분야에 해당하신다면 바로 톡톡 문의를 하시기 바랍니다.~</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-747a1090-9eb7-4779-bbe4-d2d5e4e6391f\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-\" id=\"SE-fc260352-e14b-4013-9b7a-460125fe638c\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-b7c378fe-f860-4557-a07c-253ccb5485ce\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-\" id=\"SE-b62f45ba-1051-4a07-b3e9-d1945642e163\" style=\"color:#555555;\">거래 자체가 큰 관계로 신뢰가 가장 기본이 되는 </span><span class=\"se-fs-fs24 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-bc39305f-c206-4922-843d-da111e08905d\" style=\"color:#0078cb;\"><b>부동산중개인</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-f952a05b-e074-4587-b12b-da5501639c3d\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumsquare se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-f8892ccd-6307-4e72-946b-0a40b6358375\" style=\"color:#555555;\">자신의 약력이나 시상 내용, 커리어를 표현하고 싶은 </span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-dabfba66-48b6-48d4-b63c-63b2707d5e03\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b> </b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs24 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-342e51c3-96f9-4aa0-8e81-f1d4b7d4f715\" style=\"color:#0078cb;\"><b>전문 공연 예술인</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-4438ac69-8fb1-4f80-be36-f54283916ce4\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumsquare se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-9ea3d98e-f10c-4ab0-b958-ce0c89a1a51d\" style=\"color:#555555;\">자신의 전문 분야가 확실하신 전문직 종사자</span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-2ee71947-1d03-4df6-a425-3588add11065\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b> </b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs24 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-bc272da2-a655-42a6-8231-2f0043d6d8b7\" style=\"color:#0078cb;\"><b>변호사, 의사, 변리사 등</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-eefe518d-838a-4cb3-83c2-09af4e4a8952\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumsquare se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-a736ec5d-4f36-4005-b091-d79adee8128f\" style=\"color:#555555;\">영업이 가장 중요한 홍보가 필수인 업종</span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-510ac40c-40c8-4a9e-ab7c-855e62aef93e\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b> </b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs24 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-83cb478d-8426-437c-bf79-d4d8a364790f\" style=\"color:#0078cb;\"><b>보험설계사, 자동차 딜러, 영업사원</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-ab8c0f25-c1a6-4031-b12a-df61553b3503\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs24 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-0c8ba52b-e569-4d1a-a1d0-8395517244b5\" style=\"color:#0078cb;\"><b>​</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-quotation se-l-quotation_underline\" id=\"SE-59fb44ac-2203-44dd-ab28-bdaf3d35e704\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-quotation se-l-quotation_underline\">\n<blockquote class=\"se-quotation-container\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-quote\"><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-d1a298fb-e50d-407c-bb8b-c8b72837e901\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff-\" id=\"SE-82dbc5c5-ef4e-43cd-8408-973617d41e15\" style=\"\">협업이 가능한 분야</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --></div>\n</blockquote>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-1556571e-4895-45fa-9126-9f0c57b1eb9e\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-232edde3-9c74-4efa-9ca7-6ecfc25787e1\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumsquare se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-c37c2c63-14f1-4363-bc1e-6af277bcb89c\" style=\"color:#555555;\">프로필 촬영을 전문으로 하는 </span><span class=\"se-fs-fs24 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-e227a919-fc59-4f7f-b6fe-400e3d8969c3\" style=\"color:#aa1f91;\"><b>사진업 종사자</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-14d28c51-5c6a-4ec5-b30a-0d7561e1dfdf\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumsquare se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-158bdc7d-8f7a-42bd-bda3-f7f88e1e12b8\" style=\"color:#555555;\">영업조직을 가지고 있는 상위 단계의 </span><span class=\"se-fs-fs24 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-f8c55323-9270-4f18-a12f-5f9b10834b57\" style=\"color:#aa1f91;\"><b>네트워크 마케팅 대표</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-75c1ba66-3abe-46d7-a238-569faa7f78dc\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumsquare se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-2ddfa635-a784-408f-b1a3-8b49ef574400\" style=\"color:#555555;\">모임이나 협회에서 비즈니스를 연결하는 </span><span class=\"se-fs-fs24 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-59f06a02-3824-4e62-bc0d-fc436f7eca2c\" style=\"color:#aa1f91;\"><b>전문 비즈니스 네트워크 종사자</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-0a00065a-58f7-46c0-a9f1-05003d996d6c\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-d9f35ab9-5777-4a44-b7ea-ce87bc2a5900\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>​</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-talktalk se-l-default\" id=\"SE-77dcb07f-aef8-4da8-a998-0a98de4962f0\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-talktalk se-section-align- se-l-default\">\n\n<span class=\"se-talktalk-banner-text\">\n<span class=\"se-blind\">궁금할 땐 네이버 톡톡하세요!</span>\n</span>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine se-l-default\" id=\"SE-c7d9ae21-b112-4b8a-90b5-70a3fa047d95\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-horizontalLine se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-horizontalLine\">\n<hr class=\"se-hr\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-ba402954-4a89-4c81-b1ce-90102ccf3491\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223044441442/001.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-026c802d-b93b-458d-a7c6-e49e652a0427\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-3ca212d9-e597-4422-832f-62aec3581097\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumsquare se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-9b95a5c1-bacd-4968-abdf-117886cddd9a\" style=\"color:#555555;\">완성된 프로필 명함 디자인입니다. 부동산 표시 광고 규제에 따른 프로필 명함 제작에 모든 자료와 정보를 제공해 주셨습니다. 이화부동산 김태규대표님께 다시 한번 감사의 말씀드립니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-1565af5c-42e2-43f5-899c-b0e851710006\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumsquare se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-6a23cc2e-a7ae-4b2b-8ea4-b05198f2312d\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-69ba8111-2f7d-43fa-b893-2fbf70ddc78f\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumsquare se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-9661cb76-e706-4e4b-a6e6-5ac779270176\" style=\"color:#555555;\">부동산 광고 표시 규제에 대해 궁금하시다면 다음 글을 참고해 주시기 바랍니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-ce68b7c8-e35e-4b48-8161-bb30ead8b1c9\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumsquare se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-3f7d5aa4-137e-40ff-8722-6b3b319ed4b0\" style=\"color:#555555;\"></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-df6c8c0f-06bd-4773-8745-12e83b0329f3\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumsquare se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-fc2d943f-e418-41a2-b2e7-13b816143a58\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-9acdcb0d-15d1-4887-9b3e-3f5b46fce70b\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumsquare se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-c37a0edf-1fc2-46a7-af5e-17bab108966b\" style=\"color:#555555;\">프로필 제작은 다음과 같은 자료를 전달해 주셔야 합니다. 프로필 명함이기 때문에 자신의 프로필사진이 반드시 들어가야 합니다. 하지만 간혹 사진 없이 자신의 제품이나 상품만 나열하고 싶으신 대표님도 계십니다. 그런 분들은 별도로 다른 디자인으로 제공되고 있으니 참고하시기 바랍니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-81c6bd81-0d89-4f9a-b99b-84ee33be7d6f\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-normal\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\" style=\"max-width:648px;\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223044441442/002.jpg\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-2945859a-29e1-4726-970b-00787ad4edaa\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-normal\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\" style=\"max-width:648px;\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223044441442/003.jpg\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-38be6593-0286-47a8-82b6-80c4291738b0\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-89e8ce60-f41a-4732-8a06-f818b911ab3a\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumsquare se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-13bd7aa5-8deb-4dee-a768-9464a3ceb6a3\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-d2df0ee2-7c63-4cf3-88e0-af588cc79018\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumsquare se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-b3ca537c-2144-4462-894c-8d52808a2062\" style=\"color:#555555;\">프로필명함 작업시 주셔야 하는 자료가 무엇인지 궁금할 때는 이 글을 참고하세요.</span></p><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-32a109d0-48c3-48f1-b5cd-df8383f5b2fa\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumsquare se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-cb55ee1d-9428-40a4-b4d1-3bdf73e48379\" style=\"color:#555555;\"></span></p><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-28afdf99-4879-479d-9695-9bb54077fef2\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumsquare se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-43db5b13-4243-4735-8d2e-31bed7901339\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-ea05b032-9d60-468a-bf2d-d49596b02d0a\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumsquare se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-8f53e7aa-c938-41a1-a082-ff34265ece98\" style=\"color:#555555;\">간단하게 요약하면</span></p><ol class=\"se-text-list se-text-list-type-decimal\"><li class=\"se-text-list-item\"><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-ace6062b-ed85-412e-ae40-1f7c53c24710\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumsquare se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-0c1079cd-02e6-416c-ae5f-99c833e87239\" style=\"color:#555555;\">회사 로고</span></p></li><li class=\"se-text-list-item\"><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-6a98a455-d510-46af-abe0-121ae177ed4c\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumsquare se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-eb36785d-a3ea-44e3-b965-5dd32e48570f\" style=\"color:#555555;\">상담 시간 안내</span></p></li><li class=\"se-text-list-item\"><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-db3b9d7c-0ee9-43a6-b8fa-5333bd72fa76\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumsquare se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-450506e7-64f4-4ffc-bd9b-b529d5f27efe\" style=\"color:#555555;\">주력상품 안내</span></p></li><li class=\"se-text-list-item\"><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-fc159de2-eb13-4ce6-9461-3c05b725ce33\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumsquare se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-369c0fcf-18cb-4138-9422-df8c666ef3a4\" style=\"color:#555555;\">슬로건</span></p></